testCase.name: FlakeDetector Flake Detection should detect flaky test with inconsistent results
FlakeDetector Flake Detection should mark stable test as not flaky
FlakeDetector Flake Detection should detect flaky test with occasional failures
FlakeDetector Failure Patterns should extract failure patterns
FlakeDetector Batch Flake Detection should detect multiple flaky tests
FlakeDetector Flake Summary should generate summary for multiple tests
FlakeDetector Recommendations should generate recommendations for flaky tests
FlakeDetector Parallel vs Sequential Detection should run detection in parallel when configured
